ZH: 我的房租每个月涨了一点。
EN: My rent increased a little bit every month.

ZH: 他们每月支付高昂的房租。
EN: They pay a high rent every month.

ZH: 这个城市的房租很昂贵。
EN: The rent in this city is very expensive.

ZH: 我们必须按时交房租。
EN: We must pay the rent on time.

ZH: 我每个月从工资里拿出一部分交房租。
EN: I set aside a portion of my salary every month to pay the rent.

ZH: 请把这个月的房租交给我。
EN: Please give me the rent for this month.

ZH: 我们的房租包含水电费吗？
EN: Does our rent include utilities?

ZH: 出租房子的房东提高了房租。
EN: The landlord raised the rent for the rental house.

ZH: 她找到了一个更便宜的房租。
EN: She found a cheaper rent.

ZH: 我们需要在月底交房租。
EN: We need to pay the rent at the end of the month.

ZH: 房租已经包括了煤气和水费。
EN: The rent already includes gas and water fees.

ZH: 大城市的房租较高。
EN: Rent is higher in big cities.

ZH: 这个公寓的房租很合理。
EN: The rent for this apartment is very reasonable.

ZH: 明年开始，我们将会涨房租。
EN: We will increase the rent starting next year.

ZH: 你是否可以减少一点房租？
EN: Can you lower the rent a little bit?

ZH: 我们需要签订一个房租合同。
EN: We need to sign a rental agreement.

ZH: 我们的房租包括网络费吗？
EN: Does our rent include internet fees?

ZH: 我们最近一次涨房租是几年前。
EN: The last time we raised the rent was a few years ago.

ZH: 租客们要求减少房租。
EN: The tenants are asking for a reduction in rent.

ZH: 我们必须提前一个月通知涨房租。
EN: We must give one month's notice before raising the rent.
